{"tid":1311083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】KFC中秋節推「全桶」辣雞月餅","createTime":"2019-07-13T04:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T06:14:58.000Z","uid":66271,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d926c7ee846452bfcc73a15e242a2020feb940de","tid":1311083,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3024806/org/af4b776b489c8e16909661328ae2a3a8.jpg/D8vBsMToEnCVk5xUu6AMN2kzgeXsGr4GxHObNMRzmzQ?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3024806%2Forg%2Faf4b776b489c8e16909661328ae2a3a8.jpg%2FD8vBsMToEnCVk5xUu6AMN2kzgeXsGr4GxHObNMRzmzQ%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=8a234014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每年中秋節都有不少新口味月餅登場，主打炸雞的肯德基今年都加入戰場，在facebook發帖宣布將推出「全桶」月餅的勁爆消息。KFC指新推出的月餅有兩款，分別係香辣雞絲果仁月餅及黃金流心奶皇月餅，每桶6個售價200元有找，而用以盛載的「全桶」更可變成燈籠都相當應節。部分網民對KFC都賣月餅大感詫異，辣雞月餅更特別受關注，有人笑言看到帖文第一下以為今日係愚人節，後來才發現非玩嘢po而是認真po，笑言估唔到真係有炸雞味月餅，有人就大讚算有創意會願意支持，反建議KFC做葡撻月餅或會更受歡迎。"},{"pid":"228d99d9def39d674eba002070c903bcfecd530e","tid":1311083,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6ec38441774c702cbe904e4cbbe3b2d4dd3507","tid":1311083,"uid":178332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6febe5971f9e20cd119c60c30bc83f2a19e2134a","tid":1311083,"uid":149575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e3ea6a46c3cb38622efae5fd8617de0d395c35","tid":1311083,"uid":137241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"以為愚人節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb2553129e5ed78bb10700819eb1182c5c09ec7","tid":1311083,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"冠狀動脈粥樣硬化UP☝️"},{"pid":"d2b2ea67d1756295a10b4d47337a4bd391c02c2e","tid":1311083,"uid":270986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:57:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03889bedb82e2a3c1f498110cea78194242e1ed9","tid":1311083,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"痴撚線.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過好想試一次..."},{"pid":"271684b22957bdc26665eae48b8eb7c06f028d88","tid":1311083,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"M記不如都推出巨無霸月餅啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5d2ef2a2f874b1df5a2927d561318a4e0802fb","tid":1311083,"uid":90589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:03:52.000Z","msg":"呢個年代齋玩gimmick已經賺到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都衝去試，知道難食都會有人買黎試下幾難食"},{"pid":"feba8a18c43ab2eb22e31be80a62b1ffa3e3a193","tid":1311083,"uid":122676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:09:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c724f560d1dca3b5b328323ecb4a4b9b30d66a2","tid":1311083,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcb2553129e5ed78bb10700819eb1182c5c09ec7","tid":1311083,"uid":61